item.title: GLAMOROUS
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Like always, we once again prepared to follow Puddhu Bar for the current year and into 2013. We barely had the time to finish this seasons poster that the City of Torino shut down most of the Murazzis clubs. After an ironic funeral, we can only wait for the center of the Torino nightlife to come back to life once again.
The Dreamers drumn bass is the citys venue for lovers of this genre. The 2009-2010 communication was accompanied by a series of 10 anamorphisms painted in abandoned places, a reminiscence of DnBs underground roots.

item.title: TRULEY DESIGN
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded: What I find especially successful about this campaign is a combination of well thought-out factors. One, the casting couldnt have been more spot on. Dean Wintersfrom shows like Oz and 30 Rockreally epitomizes the Mayhem persona. He wears a suit but looks like he just got out of a bar fight. Hes calm and straightforward about the destruction he causes and that matter-of-factness really hits homeespecially when Winters literally hits homes. Or cars. Or motorcycles.

item.content:encoded: What I find especially successful about this campaign is a combination of well thought-out factors. One, the casting couldnt have been more spot on. Dean Wintersfrom shows like Oz and 30 Rockreally epitomizes the Mayhem persona. He wears a suit but looks like he just got out of a bar fight. Hes calm and straightforward about the destruction he causes and that matter-of-factness really hits homeespecially when Winters literally hits homes. Or cars. Or motorcycles.
